## Notes
- Suggested strategy: `/build --strategy balanced`
- **Dual-write rule**: All new agents must be written to BOTH `~/.claude/agents/{name}.md` AND `template/.claude/agents/{name}.md`
- **Registry rule**: All new agents must have entries in `masonry/agent_registry.yml` with `tier: "draft"` and appropriate `modes` and `capabilities` fields
- **Skills path**: New skills go to `~/.claude/skills/{skill-name}/SKILL.md`
- **Hook wiring**: New hooks in masonry/src/hooks/ must be added to `~/.claude/settings.json` in the correct event section
- **Read before modify**: masonry-pre-compact.js, masonry-context-monitor.js, and uiux-master.md already exist — always read before modifying
- Phase tags on Tasks 11, 18, 20 — /build creates git tags at those points
- This is a 23-task spec — /build will run Phase 0 with pseudocode-writer and architecture-writer before task 1
